element.name: DBElement
element.descr: This package implements the DBElement<Key, Data> type, used by DBEngine < key, Value > where Value is DBElement<Key, Data>.

element.name: DBElementTest
element.descr: This package replaces DBElement test stub to remove circular package references

element.name: DBEngine
element.descr: This package implements DBEngine<Key, Value> where Value is the DBElement<key, Data> type

element.name: DBEngineTest
element.descr: This package replaces DBEngine test stub to remove circular package references

element.name: DBExtensions
element.descr: This package implements extensions methods to support displaying DBElements and DBEngine instances

element.name: DBFactory
element.descr: This package creates an immutable database from collection of keys given by QueryEngine

element.name: Display
element.descr: This package implements formatting functions and tests them along with DBExtensions

element.name: IQuery
element.descr: This package provides an interface for packages DBEngine and DBFactory

element.name: ItemFactory
element.descr: This package implements functions to add data to DBElement

element.name: PersistEngine
element.descr: This package implements functions to write data from DBEngine to XML file and vice versa.

element.name: QueryEngine
element.descr: This package implements functions to make query on DBEngine

element.name: QueryPredicate
element.descr: This package implements functions to define lambda query functions and pass them to QueryEngine package

element.name: Schedular
element.descr: This package implements functions to continuously persist data from DBEngine to XML files after specified time intervals

element.name: TestExec
element.descr: This package implements functions for the demonstration of meeting requirements.

element.name: UtilityExtensions
element.descr: This package implements utility extensions that are not specific to a single package
